    @ThreadSafe
public class RxMap<K,V extends java.io.Serializable>
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingMap<K,V>
    This class provides a concurrent map that exposes Rx subjects for put, update and remove operations on a map
    Author:
    mozessi, 1/14/2016
